Chordate:



Chordate slowly got up, putting a hand to his head.  He felt a liquid.  
Inspecting his hand, their was a blue colored liquid on his hand.  
"M...mech-fluid."  Getting up slowly, the missiles striking the Cybertronian 
Fire's shields shook the base slightly, sending Chordate slamming against a 
wall.  "Slag!" he yelled.  He searched through his data tracks.

"A beast mode!?  Of all the rotten luck!  BY THE MATRIX I HATE THOSE DAMN 
PREDACONS!  Oh, a tiger.  Well...better than if I become a damn beaver." he 
took out his laser rifle, slowly heading for the bridge, slitting every 
Predacon he came across' neck with an energon knife.
